          <a href="https://2021.jonheslop.com">2021</a>: This one was good, but
          I fell out of love with next.js
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://2017.jonheslop.com">2017</a>: this one has things in
          common with 2021
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://2012.jonheslop.com">2012</a>: this was a good one, I
